items.name: Blapature Co. Supporter 2021
items.item_description: An avocado a day keeps you healthy and curious as to where Blap-Chan went. Thank you for supporting BlapBash 2021!

items.name: Blapature Co. Benefactor 2021
items.item_description: Not only did you bring fresh avocado toast to the table, you also brought happiness to those who want to join in on the fun. Thank you for supporting BlapBash 2021!

items.name: Hexadecimal Horrors Macabre Memento 2021

items.name: Hexadecimal Horrors Moonlit Magnate 2021
items.item_description: A beacon of hope and generosity amidst the doom and gloom of the night. And endless hordes of killer robots masquerading as zombies, of course! Awarded to donors of Potato MvM's charity drive for The Trevor Project!

Binary Blackout Golden Great 2021
items.item_description: Don't let the name fool you: this canteen is made of 100% pure steel. The best we could do was paint it gold due to budgeting. Awarded to players of Moonlight MvM's winter charity tour!

items.name: Binary Blackout Silver Soldier 2021
items.item_description: Marketing accidentally wrote "silverware" instead of "silver" when commissioning these canteens. We now have a surplus of canteens made from knives and forks. Awarded to players of Moonlight MvM's winter charity tour!

items.name: Binary Blackout Bronze Beginner 2021
items.item_description: Well done rookie! Your bravery in downgrading the robot threat from "major problem" to just "problem" was recognized and has earned you this standard-issue canteen. Awarded to players of Moonlight MvM's winter charity tour!

items.name: Binary Blackout Juvenile's Jade 2021
items.item_description: You have proven that, even in the heat of battle, you can still look out for the children, and for that we award you with this neat little stone we stole from New Zealand! Awarded to donors of Moonlight MvM's winter charity tour!

items.name: Binary Blackout Marvellous Moonstone 2021
items.item_description: It's rumored that this stone was found somewhere on the moon. A more likely theory is that it's just a chunk of stained glass. Awarded to donors of Moonlight MvM's winter charity tour!

items.name: Auspicious Automaton Assembler's Accolade
items.item_description: Not everyone has what it takes to create a challenge that is also fun. Great job blowing it out of the water, merc! Awarded to content creators of Moonlight MvM's events!

items.name: Australian Hightower Highjinx Royalty 2022
items.item_description: You have managed to climb to the top of the tower in terms of your bountiful donations or your sheer competitive spirit! You've come far, soldier! Congratulations on seeing the summit, but don't forget to keep flying higher and higher. As there are many more towers to climb out there. Thanks for coming around for the AHH ride in 2022! We're Proud of you!

items.name: Australian Hightower Highjinx Participant 2022
items.item_description: You and 8 others found the will to play Hightower for the sake of pursuing in mad Highjinx, turmoil and maybe to simply have fun. Thank you for being a part of AHH in 2022!

items.name: Australian Hightower Highjinx Donor 2022
items.item_description: Whether you came to donate for a cause or show your love for Hightower you proved that you are the best of the best. Congrats on being a part of AHH in 2022!

items.name: Australian Hightower Highjinx Helper 2022
items.item_description: This medal recognizes those that kept the Highjinx under control, made sure casualties were set to a minimum, and made the cogs in the tower run smoothly through all the Highjinx in 2022!

items.item_name: Peculiar Pandemonium Tungsten Robot of Leaded Lunacy
items.item_description: Not Every Vehicular Eliminator Relies Greatly On Nonsensical Neurotic Automatons. Awarded to players of Moonlight MvM's April Fools 2022 charity tour!

items.name: Peculiar Pandemonium Luxurious Lepidolite 2022
items.item_description: Marketing surveyed our customers on which precious mineral they wanted, and everyone requested that they be pink. So we bought a few tons of the cheapest, lowest-grade lepidolite we could find and nobody was ever the wiser. Awarded to donors of Moonlight MvM's April Fools 2022 charity tour!

items.name: Peculiar Pandemonium Mesmerizing Morganite 2022
items.item_description: The Morganite is the pinnacle of gemcraft. Few people can appreciate all its value. Unfortunately, we do not represent anyone who can, so you'll have to do. Awarded to donors of Moonlight MvM's April Fools 2022 charity tour!

items.name: Peculiar Pandemonium Pink Diamond 2022
items.item_description: Formed under the immense pressure of the Earth, this gemstone has many deformations in its crystalline structure. And yet, these deformations make it all the more desirable. Awarded to donors of Moonlight MvM's April Fools 2022 charity tour!

items.item_description: You made a positive impact on TFCL, and now you've got a shiny medal to prove it!

items.name: Rewired Rampage Reverse-Engineered Ruby 2022
items.item_description: Taking a time-proven concept and flipping it on its head is no easy task, yet you managed to make it both enjoyable and memorable! Awarded to content creators of Potato MvM's Rewired Rampage campaign!

items.name: Rewired Rampage Quarrelous Quartz 2022
items.item_description: A true Gentle Manne knows that any contribution to something larger than themselves can make all the difference in the world. Awarded to donors of Potato MvM's Rewired Rampage charity event!

items.name: Rewired Rampage Perilous Peridot 2022
items.item_description: The peridot is known as the stone of compassion, and your contribution has shown that you are truly deserving of this one. Awarded to donors of Potato MvM's Rewired Rampage charity event!

items.name: Rewired Rampage Sophisticated Sapphire 2022
items.item_description: Curious onlookers at first may not notice the resilience and natural beauty of this carefully shaped stone, but you did, and for that you have been rewarded. Awarded to donors of Potato MvM's Rewired Rampage charity event!

items.name: Rewired Rampage Gem of Generosity 2022
items.item_description: You've shown yourself to be a beacon of generosity no matter the circumstances. Let this flawless gemstone serve as just one example of your altruism. Awarded to donors of Potato MvM's Rewired Rampage charity event!

Anniversary Annihilation Participation Trophy 2022
items.item_description: We would congratulate you on your efforts, but you didn't exactly do much to get a pat on the back. So instead, try to enjoy this rusted metal on that scrawny chest of yours. Awarded to players of Moonlight MvM's summer charity tour!

items.name: Anniversary Annihilation Galvanized Goblet 2022
items.item_description: You didn't think we'd send you into an army of robots without a reward, would you? Just for you, we have some spare galvanized beauties that were definitely not taken off dead mercs who failed before you. Awarded to players of Moonlight MvM's summer charity tour!

items.name: Anniversary Annihilation Soul-Binding Star 2022
items.item_description: Many have tried to capture the soul of a mission in the form of a gemstone, but the stone always breaks upon capturing a single mission. This star-shaped stone, however, is capable of holding the souls of every mission in this event. Awarded to players of Moonlight MvM's summer charity tour!

items.name: Anniversary Annihilation Caregiving Corundum 2022
items.item_description: While we don't give credit, you came back when you were richer and gave some of that wealth to help out animals in need. Awarded to donors of Moonlight MvM's summer charity tour!

items.name: Anniversary Annihilation Heroistic Heart 2022
items.item_description: Your bottomless heart has assisted many animals in need, and while we couldn't revive the yetis Hale punched into extinction, you did your part for the remaining animals. Awarded to donors of Moonlight MvM's summer charity tour!

items.name: Anniversary Annihilation Dastardly Diamond 2022
items.item_description: The legendary accursed diamond is the subject of countless mythologies. This isn't that diamond; it's just something our specially trained truffle hogs sniffed out of a diamond mine in Arkansas. Awarded to donors of Moonlight MvM's summer charity tour!

items.name: TF2Maps Ray of Sunshine 2022
items.item_description: Make 'em happy when skies are gray. Awarded to donors during the TF2Maps 72hr TF2Jam 2022!

items.name: Blapature Co. Backer 2022
items.item_description: The most important thing when making jam is ignoring the defeated stares from your loved ones as you serve it for the seventh week in a row. Thank you for supporting BlapBash 2022!

items.name: Blapature Co. Supporter 2022
items.item_description: An avocado a day ain't much, but it's honest fruit. Thank you for supporting BlapBash 2022!

items.name: Blapature Co. Benefactor 2022
items.item_description: When your brand surrounds avocados, be prepared to love Avocado toast for breakfast, lunch, dinner, and to cherish, until parted by financial death. Thank you for supporting BlapBash 2022!

items.name: Blapature Co. Advocator 2022
items.item_description: The best kind of jam is made from aged avocados. Thank you for supporting BlapBash 2022!
